{"tid":1468372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家無做錯到!劇本一早寫好，只係遲左一日","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:45:35.000Z","uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c9be5baa62c2b7b3576df41b2025edf4805eff76","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:16.000Z","msg":"相信大家前日行路上廣州都肯<br />\n而封橋取消班次提早疏散<br />\n其實劇本一早已內定<br />\n只不過散哂水做唔到野<br />\n而今日就只係將應該發生既野推遲左一日<br />\n所有野都係收錢毅進仔推出黎<br />\n捉鬼真係無問題<br />\n但如果真係捉錯左人<br />\n咁岩又比d鬼踢左個遊客幾下<br />\n我地只有硬食<br />\nbtw新禁令大家再研究"},{"pid":"cd55187ae5fcf55d0a5993a1ec3ce06cadbc948d","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"663e94f27549f67fb48a9249e8e450cd0a2a61e4","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:15.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"121129cdf1cbc1ed1dbba61400f3eaeed03c0666","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"a53b6f91326677428abe5b160f5bf273b8a15f46","tid":1468372,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"係 劇本遲左一日<br />\n長期係機場實不斷搞鳩你"},{"pid":"3779b790e49cdb161d8866de458a92ce723f45c3","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"d196610267de32b607d7105dd55b403c0d064dc5","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:29:15.000Z","msg":"不分化不割"},{"pid":"0323984dc2397e3bdbb1d8e186c17e148a12c07d","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"8d6cb294d76de2b5c809c3a1d816cded6f30d2d3","tid":1468372,"uid":292783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:32:17.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"636f7f1f3848616f679c7